extends layout
block append headExtender
	link(rel="stylesheet", href="/stylesheets/index.css")

block content
	div#indexHeader
		h1 SSRF DETECTOR
	hr
	div.row
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-md-offset-2.why
			h2 Why?
			p External server-side request forgery is a hassle to detect, so I created the SSRF Detector.  Grab your own Blinkie subdomain and use that for all of your SSRF testing, you will receive an email when any requests are successful.  Also check out the 
				a(href="/dashboard")
					| dashboard 
				| to see your 10 most recent Detections.
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.why
			h2 SSR(WT)F?!
			p For a great explanation of what server-side request forgery is please go 
				a(href="https://www.bishopfox.com/blog/2015/04/vulnerable-by-design-understanding-server-side-request-forgery/", target="_blank")
					| here
	div.row
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-md-offset-2.why
			h2 How do I start?
			div.video-container
				iframe(width='560', height='315', src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/M9k6LxNk2bM', frameborder='0', allowfullscreen='')
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.why
			h2 Can I buy you a cup of coffee?
			p Absolutely!  I fund all of this myself, so I appreciate any help at all.  You can buy me a cup of coffee or pay for some server time below. 
				form(action='https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr', method='post', target='_top').text-center
					input(type='hidden', name='cmd', value='_s-xclick')
					input(type='hidden', name='encrypted', value='-----BEGIN PKCS7----------END PKCS7-----\
  				')
					input(type='image', src='https://static1.squarespace.com/static/528e97bbe4b0e2f77a6e1455/t/5293fa7ae4b0f601b40ec24e/1385429627883/Donatebutton.png', border='0', name='submit', alt='PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!', height="50")
					img(alt='', border='0', src='https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif', width='1', height='1')
	div.row
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-md-offset-2.why
			h2 Having problems?
			p Feel free to contact me at jreynoldsdev(at)gmail.com.
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.why
			h2 Thanks
			p Special thanks to 
				a(href="https://xsshunter.com", target="_blank")
					| XSS Hunter
				|  for the inspiration.
	div.row
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-md-offset-2.why.sucks
			h2 Why is the UI so terrible?
			p Because I'm terrible at UI design.
		div.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4.why
			h2 I'm Ron Burgundy?
			p That's enough with the questions.  View the source code 
				a(href="https://github.com/jacobreynolds/ssrfdetector", target="_blank")
					| here

